title: Demonstrators celebrating Mubārak's resignation
description: The demonstrators are waving Egyptian flags and lighting makeshift blow torches in Mīdān Victoria. Phototgraphers' description: photos and video of Jan 29-Feb 11, 2011, Protests (downtown) & celebration in Maadi.
